            "EN": "You may not be using your time effectively, taking less important tasks first and leaving most important untouched. You may also be experiencing a problem with an accumulation of material to work through. Related to this is the difficulty in remembering content for longer and experiencing stress that the material is unmanageable. Brilliant works require not only an idea, talent, but above all effort and time. The result of a lack of concentration is mistakes, forgetting details, overlooking or under-performing.",
