        "description": {
            "PL": "To jest bardzo wa\u017cny obszar! Opisuje on g\u0142\u00f3wne tendencje poznawcze zwi\u0105zane z rozwojem, uczeniem si\u0119. Tutaj znajduj\u0105 si\u0119 opisy dotycz\u0105ce motywacji wewn\u0119trznej, nastawienia na osi\u0105ganie cel\u00f3w, ambicj\u0119. Wyniki tego obszaru mo\u017cna powiaza\u0107 z umiej\u0119tno\u015bciami kojarzenia, abstrakcyjnego my\u015blenia, umiej\u0119tno\u015bci uczenia si\u0119 wielu informacji na raz. Wed\u0142ug naszego podej\u015bcia od tego ile faktycznie wysi\u0142ku jeste\u015bmy gotowi ponie\u015b\u0107 i ile ponosimy w celu zrozumienia tre\u015bci, powi\u0105za\u0144 mi\u0119dzy nimi, zale\u017cy sukces edukacyjny.",
            "EN": "This is a\u00a0prime\u00a0area! It describes the main cognitive\u00a0orientations\u00a0related to development\u00a0and\u00a0learning. Here you will find descriptions\u00a0of\u00a0intrinsic motivation, goal orientation\u00a0and\u00a0ambition.\u00a0Results\u00a0in this area can be linked to association skills, abstraction and the ability to learn a lot of information at once. According to our approach, educational success depends on how much effort we are actually prepared to make and\u00a0on our ability to understand the contents and to articulate them.",
            "FR": "C'est un domaine de premier ordre ! Il d\u00e9crit les principales orientations cognitives li\u00e9es au d\u00e9veloppement et \u00e0 l'apprentissage. Vous trouverez ici des descriptions concernant la motivation intrins\u00e8que, l'orientation choisie en fonction d'objectifs et de l'ambition. Les r\u00e9sultats dans ce domaine peuvent \u00eatre li\u00e9s aux capacit\u00e9s d'association, d\u2019abstraction et \u00e0 la capacit\u00e9 d'apprendre beaucoup d'informations \u00e0 la fois. Selon notre approche, la r\u00e9ussite scolaire d\u00e9pend de l'effort que nous sommes r\u00e9ellement pr\u00eats \u00e0 fournir ainsi que de notre capacit\u00e9 \u00e0 comprendre les contenus et de les articuler entre eux."
        },
        "impact": {
            "PL": "Obszar ten wp\u0142ywa na to czy ucze\u0144 jest otwarty na now\u0105 wiedz\u0119, do\u015bwiadczenia, czy trzyma si\u0119 tego co ju\u017c zna, umie. Im mniej wysi\u0142ku jest w stanie w\u0142o\u017cy\u0107, tym mniej czasu/pracy po\u015bwi\u0119ci na zapami\u0119tywanie oraz przetwarzanie informacji. Wy\u017csze wyniki s\u0105 powi\u0105zane z ambicjami, poszukiwaniem nowych tre\u015bci, osi\u0105gni\u0119ciami.",
            "EN": "This area influences whether the student is open to new knowledge, experiences, whether he sticks to what he already knows, knows how to do. The less effort he/she is able to put in, the less time/work he/she will spend memorising and processing information. Higher performance is linked to ambition, the search for new content, achievement.\u00a0\u00a0PROP : This area indicates whether the student is open to new knowledge and new experiences or if he/she tends to stick to what he/she already knows and can do. In practical terms, the less effort a student is able to make, the less time and work he or she will dedicate to memorizing and processing information. In the opposite case, higher performance is related to a higher intrinsic level of ambition, as well as effort in the search for new content and personal investment in achievement.",
            "FR": "Ce domaine indique si l'\u00e9l\u00e8ve est ouvert \u00e0 de nouvelles connaissances et \u00e0 de nouvelles exp\u00e9riences ou s'il a propension \u00e0 se cantonner \u00e0 ce qu'il sait d\u00e9j\u00e0 et \u00e0 ce qu'il sait d\u00e9j\u00e0 faire. Concr\u00eatement, moins l'\u00e9l\u00e8ve est en mesure de fournir d'efforts, moins il consacrera de temps et de travail \u00e0 la m\u00e9morisation et au traitement de l\u2019information. Dans le cas contraire, des performances plus \u00e9lev\u00e9es sont li\u00e9es \u00e0 un degr\u00e9 intrins\u00e8que d\u2019ambition plus \u00e9lev\u00e9, ainsi que d'effort dans la recherche de nouveaux contenus et d'investissement personnel en mati\u00e8re de r\u00e9ussite."
        },
        "benefits": {
            "PL": "Rozw\u00f3j tego obszaru to wi\u0119ksza motywacja wewn\u0119trzna, starania o osi\u0105gni\u0119cie sukcesu. Poznawczo oznacza to wi\u0119ksze mo\u017cliwo\u015bci pozyskiwania informacji, zapami\u0119tywania i przetwarzania.",
            "EN": "Development of this area means more intrinsic motivation, efforts to succeed. Cognitively, it means greater ability to acquire information, remember and process.\u00a0PROP:Strengthening this area means increasing one's level of intrinsic motivation and willingness to put in effort to succeed. Cognitively, it means increasing one's ability to store informations, process them and articulate them together.",
            "FR": "Renforcer ce domaine signifie accro\u00eetre son niveau de motivation intrins\u00e8que et sa volont\u00e9 \u00e0 fournir des efforts pour r\u00e9ussir. Sur le plan cognitif, cela signifie augmenter sa capacit\u00e9 \u00e0 emmagasiner des informations, \u00e0 les traiter et \u00e0 les faire articuler entre-elles."
        },
