                    "PL": "Kiedy ucze\u0144/uczennica traci z oczu sw\u00f3j cel, przestaje podejmowa\u0107 wysi\u0142ki, aby go osi\u0105gn\u0105\u0107, a wi\u0119c nie realizuje ju\u017c swojego planu.",
                    "EN": "When you lose sight of your goal, you stop making efforts to achieve it, so you no longer follow your plan.\u00a0PROP:When the student's mental state drops and he/she loses sight of the goal, he/she stops striving to achieve his/her goals and no longer follows the assigned plan.",
                    "FR": "Lorsque l\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l\u2019\u00e9tudiant a une baisse de moral et perd de vue son objectif il/elle cesse\u00a0\u00a0de faire des efforts pour atteindre ses objectifs et il/elle ne suit plus le plan qui lui \u00e9tait assign\u00e9."
