                    "PL": "Ucze\u0144/Uczennica czasem rezygnuje z pr\u00f3b ustalenia, czego nie potrafi zrobi\u0107 (np. \u0107wicze\u0144, sportu, sk\u0142adania mebli).",
                    "EN": "I sometimes give up trying to figure out what I can't do (e.g., an exercise, a sport, putting together a piece of furniture).\u00a0PROP:The student sometimes gives up trying to understand what he/she cannot immediately achieve (e.g., an exercise, an activity, a sport).",
                    "FR": "L\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l\u2019\u00e9tudiant renonce parfois \u00e0 essayer de comprendre ce qu\u2019il/elle n\u2019arrive pas imm\u00e9diatement \u00e0 r\u00e9aliser comme par exemple un exercice, une activit\u00e9, un sport quelconque)."
