                            "EN": "Develop empathy for other people's situations to better understand them.\u00a0PROP:The student should reflexively ask someone close to them to try to understand what motivated them to achieve their goals in this way. This is a good way to discuss methodology with others.",
                            "FR": "L\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l\u2019\u00e9tudiant doit d\u00e9velopper de l\u2019empathie face aux situations que les autres vivent de cette mani\u00e8re il pourra mieux les comprendre."
