                            "EN": "Ask someone close to you to try to understand your motivation for doing your goals in this way. This is a good way to discuss your methodology with others.\u00a0PROP:The student should make plans and set goals based on his/her dreams. He/she should not give up on the world that he/she would like to create for him/herself.",
