                    "EN": "I am often not interested in new music, movies, events. I have a very structured lifestyle with the same habits. PROP: The student is often not interested in the new things of his/her generation (music, movies, events). He/she tends to stick to a very ascetic lifestyle in which he/she maintains strict habits.",
                    "FR": "L\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l\u2019\u00e9tudiant n\u2019est souvent pas int\u00e9ress\u00e9 par les nouveaut\u00e9s de sa g\u00e9n\u00e9ration (musique, films, \u00e9v\u00e9nements). Il/elle a tendance \u00e0 se cantonner \u00e0 un style de vie tr\u00e8s asc\u00e9tique dans lequel il/elle maintient des habitudes strictes."
