                            "EN": "Make your plans and set your goals according to your dreams. Don't give up on the world you want for yourself.\u00a0PROP: The student needs to understand why he/she tends not to focus on the essentials of what he/she is learning. What can he/she change in his/her attitude or way of learning?",
                            "FR": "L\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l\u2019\u00e9tudiant devrait faire des plans et se fixer des objectifs en fonction de ses r\u00eaves. Il/elle ne devrait pas renoncer au monde qu\u2019il/elle aimerait se cr\u00e9er."
