                            "EN": "Find other sources of knowledge (such as films, newspapers, original explanations) and ask your teachers for specific tips according to your needs.PROP:The student should seek out other sources of knowledge (such as films, newspapers, original explanations) and then ask their teachers for specific guidance based on their needs.",
                            "FR": "L\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l\u2019\u00e9tudiant devrait rechercher d'autres sources de connaissances (comme des films, des journaux, des explications originales) puis devrait demander \u00e0 ses professeurs des conseils sp\u00e9cifiques en fonction de ses besoins."
