                    "EN": "I have a hard time remembering certain course content for a long time. I don't pay attention to the basics when I study.\u00a0PROP:The student has difficulty remembering the content of some of his/her lessons for a long time. He/she does not pay attention to the details that would allow him/her to remember the essential.",
                    "FR": "L\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l\u2019\u00e9tudiant a du mal \u00e0 se rappeler longtempes des contenus de certains de ses cours. Il/elle ne fais \u00e0 attention aux d\u00e9tails qui lui permettrait de se souvenir de l\u2019essentiel."
