                            "EN": "Understand why you tend not to focus on the basics of what you are learning. What can you change about your attitude or the way you learn?\u00a0PROP: The student should remind himself/herself why he/she wants to achieve his/her goal, even if he/she does not yet see any real progress. If he/she has chosen his/her project well according to his/her ambitions, he/she must inevitably succeed. Perhaps he/she should adapt his/her practices and way of acting. This reflection invites him/her to think about the way he/she approaches his/her projects.",
                            "FR": "L\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l\u2019\u00e9tudiant doit comprendre pourquoi il/elle a tendance \u00e0 ne pas se concentrer sur l\u2019essentiel de ce qu\u2019il/elle apprend. Que peut-il/elle changer dans son attitude ou dans sa fa\u00e7on d\u2019apprendre ?"
