                    "PL": "Ucznia/Uczennicy nie interesuje to, jak rzeczy dzia\u0142aj\u0105, nie interesuj\u0105 go/jej problemy zbyt abstrakcyjne, ani problemy polityczne i spo\u0142eczne.",
                    "EN": "I am not interested in how things work, nor in problems that are too abstract, nor in political and social problems.\u00a0PROP:The student is not interested in how his/her environment works. He/she shows little interest in problems that are too abstract or political and social.",
                    "FR": "L\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l\u2019\u00e9tudiant ne s\u2019int\u00e9resse pas \u00e0 la mani\u00e8re dont son environnement fonctionne. Il/elle d\u00e9montre peu d\u2019int\u00e9r\u00eats pour les probl\u00e8mes trop abstraits ou encore politiques et sociaux."
