                    "EN": "I get bored a lot in class, I don't find the course content interesting and I lose the flow of the course quickly.\u00a0PROP: The student is very bored in class, he/she does not find the content of the courses interesting and often loses the thread of the course.",
                    "FR": "L\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l\u2019\u00e9tudiant s\u2019ennuie beaucoup en classe, il/elle ne trouve pas le contenu des cours int\u00e9ressants et perd souvent le fil des cours."
