                            "EN": "Motivate yourself by setting up your own reward system. Define your rules, goals and rewards after you make progress and achieve key steps in your project.\u00a0PROP: The student should motivate him/herself by setting up his/her own reward system. He/she should define his/her rules, goals and rewards for progressing and achieving milestones.",
