                    "PL": "Ucze\u0144/Uczennica w obliczu z\u0142o\u017conego wyzwania, kt\u00f3rego nie potrafi rozwi\u0105za\u0107, szuka kogo\u015b, kto Jemu/Jej pomo\u017ce lub wykona zadanie za Niego/Ni\u0105, albo porzuca kontynuowanie wyzwania.",
                    "EN": "Faced with a complex challenge that I can't solve, I look for someone to help me or to do the task for me, or I give up pursuing the challenge.\u00a0PROP:The student tends to seek help when faced with a seemingly unsolvable problem. He/she will try to find someone willing to help or to perform the task for him/her. If he/she cannot find someone he/she gives up the challenge.",
