                    "PL": "Styl \u017cycia ucznia/uczennicy jest ma\u0142o zr\u00f3wnowa\u017cony, nie \u0107wiczy zbyt wiele w ci\u0105gu dnia i ma\u0142o si\u0119 rusza.",
                    "EN": "My lifestyle is not very balanced, I don't exercise much during the day and I don't move around much.\u00a0PROP:The student has a lifestyle that is not very balanced in terms of physical activity. He/she does not exercise much during the day and avoids walking.",
