                            "EN": "For his/her personal balance, the student must learn to listen and respect his/her needs.",
                            "FR": "Pour son \u00e9quilibre personnel, l'\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l'\u00e9tudiant doit apprendre \u00e0 \u00e9couter et \u00e0 respecter ses besoins."
