                    "PL": "Ucze\u0144/Uczennica chcia\u0142by/chcia\u0142aby dostawa\u0107 dobre stopnie i oceny, nie wk\u0142adaj\u0105c w to wiele pracy. Czasami zadowala si\u0119 minimum w klasie, \u017ceby tylko przebrn\u0105\u0107 przez rok. Nie zale\u017cy mu/jej na sukcesie, chocia\u017c wie, \u017ce potrafi si\u0119 bardzo stara\u0107.",
                    "EN": "The student would like to get good grades and good evaluations without having to make any effort. He/she feels a certain dullness in his/her school work. He/she is satisfied with the minimum in class, just to pass the year. He/she doesn't really care about excelling in his/her field even though he/she knows he/she can make an effort.",
                    "FR": "L\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l\u2019\u00e9tudiant aimerait obtenir de bonne notes et de bonnes appr\u00e9ciations sans avoir \u00e0 fournir d\u2019efforts. Il/elle \u00e9prouve une certaine lassitude dans son travail scolaire. Il/elle se contente du minimum en classe, juste pour passer l\u2019ann\u00e9e. Il/elle ne se soucie pas vraiment d\u2019exceller dans son domaine m\u00eame si il/elle sait qu\u2019il/elle peut fournir des efforts."
