                            "EN": "The student should regularly participate in a sport that helps him/her develop self-confidence. Some team sports such as volleyball or individual sports such as fencing can help in this regard.",
                            "FR": "L'\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l'\u00e9tudiant doit pratiquer r\u00e9guli\u00e8rement un sport qui l'aide \u00e0 d\u00e9velopper sa confiance en lui/elle. Certains sports d'\u00e9quipe comme le volley-ball ou des sports individuels comme l'escrime peuvent l'aider en ce sens."
