                            "EN": "The student should be encouraged to start the day by completing the important tasks he/she needs to do. This will avoid the risk of not having done enough at the end of the day.",
                            "FR": "L\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve/l\u2019\u00e9tudiant doit \u00eatre encourg\u00e9(e) \u00e0 commencer sa journ\u00e9e en accomplissant les t\u00e2ches importantes qu\u2019il/elle doit accomplir. Cela lui \u00e9vitera le risque de ne pas  avoir fait assez \u00e0 la fin de la journ\u00e9e."
