                    "EN": "In unexpected or surprising situations, it is difficult for the student to take stock and analyze the situation to find an innovative solution.",
                    "FR": "Dans des situations inattendues ou surprenantes, l\u2019\u00e9tudiant(e) a du mal \u00e0 faire le point et \u00e0 analyser la situation pour y trouver une solution innovante."
