                    "PL": "Ucze\u0144/Uczennica, kiedy staje przed problemem, ma tendencj\u0119 do \u0142atwego poddawania si\u0119.",
                    "EN": "When faced with a problem, the student tends to give up easily.",
                    "FR": "Lorsque l\u2019\u00e9tudiant(e) est confront\u00e9(e) \u00e0 un probl\u00e8me, il/elle a tendance \u00e0 abandonner facilement."
