                    "EN": "The student values certain rituals in his/her life, habits related to his/her way of living, to his/her way of behaving, such as: taking the same path, preparing his/her meal or having his/her favorite dessert after school.\u00a0\u00a0It is sometimes difficult for him/her to find him/herself in new situations and to do things that he/she has never done before.",
