                    "EN": "The student tends to believe that he/she is not capable of accomplishing anything. There are times when he/she does not believe in his/her ability to achieve his/her goals.",
                    "FR": "L'\u00e9tudiant(e) a tendance \u00e0 croire qu'il/elle n'est pas capable d'accomplir quoi que ce soit. Il y a des moments o\u00f9 il/elle ne croit pas en sa capacit\u00e9 \u00e0 atteindre ses objectifs."
