                    "EN": "In different situations, for example in the field of sports, the student sometimes thinks that he/she can beat the race record (even if this is not realistic) or other times he/she immediately gives up what he/she is doing or lowers his/her ambitions and considers it a success to at least finish what he/she has started. He/she lacks discernment in analyzing the situations he/she encounters.",
