        "name": {
            "PL": "Wsp\u00f3\u0142praca na rzecz wsp\u00f3lnego celu. Konstruktywna dyskusja i konfrontacja. Elastyczno\u015b\u0107 my\u015blenia i szeroka perspektywa.",
            "EN": "Collaboration to achieve common goals. Constructive discussions and confrontations. Open-mindedness and broadening of perspectives.",
            "FR": "Collaboration \u00e0 la r\u00e9alisation d'objectifs communs. Discussions et confrontations constructives. Ouverture d'esprit et \u00e9largissement des perspectives."
        },
        "description": {
            "PL": "Wsp\u00f3\u0142praca to nie tylko zaufanie do innych i gotowo\u015b\u0107 pomagania. Wa\u017cnym aspektem jest wiara w to, \u017ce wsp\u00f3lnie mo\u017cna osi\u0105gn\u0105\u0107 wi\u0119cej. Za tym b\u0119d\u0105 sz\u0142y r\u00f3wnie\u017c starania, by grupa/klasa stawa\u0142a si\u0119 lepsza. Praca z innymi daje du\u017co przyjemno\u015bci, poczucie przynale\u017cno\u015b\u0107i, wzmacnia pewno\u015b\u0107 siebie. Z innej perspektywy patrz\u0105c obszar ten opisuje elastyczno\u015b\u0107 my\u015blenia, szeroko\u015b\u0107 perspektywy. Dzi\u0119ki temu ucze\u0144/uczennica rozumie wi\u0119cej, postrzega wi\u0119cej opcji. Ostatni aspekt to o\u015b rywalizacja - wsp\u00f3\u0142praca. W r\u00f3\u017cnych sytuacjach taka postawa przyniesie r\u00f3\u017cne konsekwencje.",
            "EN": "'Cooperation is not just about trusting others and being willing to help them. An important aspect to consider is the belief that by acting together those present can achieve better results. Efforts should also be made to improve the understanding within the group/class. Working with others provides a great sense of enjoyment, generates a sense of belonging and builds self-confidence. It allows the student to understand more, to see more opportunities and to have more confidence in him/herself. The last aspect to consider is the competitive-collaborative. Depending on the context, this attitude that goes beyond collaboration and results in competition between students will have different consequences.",
            "FR": "La coop\u00e9ration ne consiste pas seulement \u00e0 faire confiance aux autres et \u00e0 \u00eatre pr\u00eat \u00e0 les aider. Un aspect important \u00e0 prendre en compte est la conviction qu\u2019en agissant ensemble les personnes pr\u00e9sentes peuvent obtenir de meilleurs r\u00e9sultats. Des efforts sont \u00e9galement \u00e0 fournir en vue d\u2019am\u00e9liorer l\u2019entente au sein du groupe/de la classe. Travailler avec les autres procure beaucoup de plaisir permet de g\u00e9n\u00e9rer un sentiment d'appartenance et de renforcer la confiance en soi. Cela permet \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9tudiant(e) de comprendre davantage, d\u2019entrevoir plus d'opportunit\u00e9s et d'avoir une meilleure confiance en lui/elle-m\u00eame. Le dernier axe \u00e0 prendre en compte est le comp\u00e9titif-collaboratif. En fonction du contexte, cette attitude qui d\u00e9passe la simple collaboration et qui occasionne la comp\u00e9tition entre les \u00e9tudiant(e)s aura des cons\u00e9quences diff\u00e9rentes."
        },
        "impact": {
            "PL": "Czynnik ten wp\u0142ywa na umiej\u0119tno\u015b\u0107 wsp\u00f3\u0142pracy zespo\u0142owej i tego, czy ucze\u0144/uczennica umie korzysta\u0107 z bycia z innymi. Czynnik wp\u0142ywa te\u017c na umiej\u0119no\u015b\u0107 trafnej argumentacji, docierania do innych i czerpania od innych. Nieod\u0142\u0105czn\u0105 cz\u0119\u015bci\u0105 b\u0119dzie zatem umiej\u0119tno\u015b\u0107 kompromisu i wsp\u00f3\u0142pracy, a tak\u017ce konstruktywnego dzia\u0142ania w sytuacji sporu.",
            "EN": "This factor determines the ability to cooperate as a team and whether the student knows how to benefit from the presence of others. This factor also affects the ability to debate fairly, to approach others and to learn from others. As well as, the ability to compromise, cooperate and act constructively in conflict situations.",
            "FR": "Ce facteur d\u00e9termine la capacit\u00e9 \u00e0 coop\u00e9rer en \u00e9quipe et permet de savoir si l\u2019\u00e9tudiant(e) sait comment tirer profit de la pr\u00e9sence des autres. Ce facteur affecte \u00e9galement la capacit\u00e9 \u00e0 d\u00e9battre avec justesse, \u00e0 aller vers les autres et \u00e0 apprendre des autres. Ainsi que, la capacit\u00e9 \u00e0 faire des compromis, \u00e0 coop\u00e9rer et \u00e0 agir de mani\u00e8re constructive dans des situations de conflit."
        },
        "benefits": {
            "PL": "Wysokie umiej\u0119tno\u015bci i postawy w tym obszarze b\u0119d\u0105 charakteryzowa\u0142y osob\u0119 buduj\u0105c\u0105 grup\u0119/zesp\u00f3\u0142, kt\u00f3ra konstruktywnie b\u0119dzie zachowywa\u0107 si\u0119 w sytuacji konfliktu, b\u0119dzie zach\u0119ca\u0107 do wsp\u00f3\u0142pracy. Ucze\u0144/uczennica b\u0119dzie mia\u0142/mia\u0142a umiej\u0119tno\u015b\u0107 empatii i troski o innych. Raczej b\u0119dzie unika\u0107 spor\u00f3w i rywalizacji rozumianej jako walk\u0119 tylko o sw\u00f3j punkt widzenia.",
            "EN": "A high score in this area, demonstrates leadership skills and abilities. The student as leader will behave constructively in conflict situations and encourage cooperation.\u00a0\u00a0The student will have the ability to show empathy and concern for others. He/she will prefer to avoid arguments and rivalry, opting for communication in resolving disputes.",
            "FR": "Un score \u00e9lev\u00e9 dans ce domaine, d\u00e9montre des comp\u00e9tences et aptitudes au leadership. L\u2019\u00e9tudiant(e) en tant que leader se comportera de mani\u00e8re constructive dans les situations de conflit et encouragera la coop\u00e9ration.\u00a0\u00a0L'\u00e9tudiant(e) aura la capacit\u00e9 \u00e0 faire preuve d'empathie et \u00e0 se soucier des autres. Il/elle pr\u00e9f\u00e9rera \u00e9viter les disputes et la rivalit\u00e9, optera pour la communication dans la r\u00e9solutions de diff\u00e9rends."
        },
