                            "EN": "High intelligence and a good memory sometimes prevent mastery of a skill - because one does not want to practice. The student must be aware of the amount of effort involved because it is habits and hard work that determine the outcome of a project. Therefore, he/she must complete the required tasks/exercises and practice!",
