                    "PL": "Uczniowi/Uczennicy brakuje wnikliwo\u015bci, gdy ocenia siebie. W niekt\u00f3rych sytuacjach nawet jego/jej emocje mog\u0105 zniekszta\u0142ci\u0107 jego/jej os\u0105d.",
                    "EN": "The student sometimes lacks insight into his/her abilities. He/she is unable to evaluate him/herself objectively. The intensity of his/her emotions sometimes clouds his/her thinking and prevents him/her from finding adequate solutions.",
