                    "EN": "Sometimes the student only wants to get good grades and the best evaluations, without making a real effort to do so. On the other hand, sometimes the student is content with borderline bad grades just to get through the year. He/she does not care about succeeding, even though he/she knows that he/she could make more effort and get better grades.",
