                            "EN": "Ensure that your understanding of situations and phenomena can be transferred into concrete actions. Sometimes it is also important for others to understand what seems obvious to you.                           Support your child in transferring his/her understanding of situations and phenomena into concrete actions. Sensitise your child that it is important for others to understand what you take for granted.",
                            "FR": "Veillez \u00e0 ce que votre compr\u00e9hension des situations et des ph\u00e9nom\u00e8nes puisse \u00eatre transpos\u00e9e en actions concr\u00e8tes. Parfois, il est \u00e9galement important que les autres comprennent ce qui vous semble \u00e9vident. Aidez votre enfant \u00e0 transposer sa compr\u00e9hension des situations et des ph\u00e9nom\u00e8nes en actions concr\u00e8tes. Sensibilisez votre enfant au fait qu'il est important que les autres comprennent ce que vous consid\u00e9rez comme acquis."
