            "EN": "This area influences whether the child is open to new knowledge, experiences, whether he sticks to what he already knows, knows how to do. The less effort he/she is able to put in, the less time/work he/she will spend memorising and processing information. Higher performance is linked to ambition, the search for new content, achievement.",
