                            "EN": "Setting out a career plan requires planning a number of structuring steps. The first is to determine your personal needs, your desires, your essential motivations. It is on this basis that we can then determine the necessary qualifications and consider the next phases. Our limits are often imposed by our anxieties and not by our desires, which are the drivers of our potential.",
