                            "EN": "Encourage your team to seek feedback on the qaulity of their work from superiors, co-workers and colleagues  more often and to consider the overall effect of their work. This will allow them to maintain an objective view of the situation. Too much attention to detail can sometimes make our analysis too subjective.",
